{"tid":1644560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由今日開始唔會再帶口罩","createTime":"2019-10-10T15:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:31:30.000Z","uid":231299,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5adac1bddc860c222f5255eb08a91d4eb416f8d","tid":1644560,"uid":231299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"反正全民口罩日得個講字，作為一個學生日日on99咁單機帶住個口罩唔知做乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒未呀你班偽善嘅香港人，由六月到依家反抗嘅熱誠去哂邊？<br />\n手足比人射眼，射心口都完全沒感覺繼續第二日返工就算？你對唔對得住佢哋，只係立左一個蒙面法就個個驚比人拉，我身為一個學生，可能係唔夠膽上前線勇武，但我哋係唔係應該都至少做返少少嘢去對抗白色恐怖？我一個學生仔都肯去帶口罩，你哋呢？希望可以見到更多同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb320e61ad5ef97a960cabe50fb47f47cc66ef6","tid":1644560,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"不如set一日做口罩日，之後再日常搞?<br />\n<br />\n利申會繼續keep住做"},{"pid":"4a223a14296797e19c97189ca210b0c0d7e9e8c9","tid":1644560,"uid":231299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cb320e61ad5ef97a960cabe50fb47f47cc66ef6","tid":1644560,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:03:07.000Z","msg":"不如set一日做口罩日，之後再日常搞?<br />\n<br />\n利申會繼續keep住做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"本身星期二都已經講左係全民口罩日，成效完全睇唔出"},{"pid":"52de6325a42094686f4f3112e7e8112add3e1645","tid":1644560,"uid":275950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"全民對抗伊波拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d1976f692daaf4b05a00fcb56e5ed09df6e642","tid":1644560,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"偽善嘅香港人"},{"pid":"9c06ed854edbbe3b107c137d6881b82ec959e0fb","tid":1644560,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:31:30.000Z","m